00:41:16.557 --> 00:41:19.769  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:61.43%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Either way, it's up to you.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1323
00:41:25.108 --> 00:41:31.948  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:55.71%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Well... it seems I won't</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1324
00:41:25.108 --> 00:41:31.948  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:55.71%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>be needing this anymore.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1325
00:41:42.208 --> 00:41:45.086  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:53.81%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>(</c.mono_sans></c.white><i><c.white><c.mono_sans> sighing contentedly )</c.mono_sans></c.white></i>

1326
00:41:48.923 --> 00:41:51.134  position:44.29%,start  align:start size:19.52%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>So...</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1327
00:41:51.134 --> 00:41:53.470  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:69.05%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>what shall we talk about first?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1328
00:42:10.278 --> 00:42:11.612  position:40.48%,start  align:start size:27.14%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Just you?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1329
00:42:11.612 --> 00:42:12.864  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:50.00%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I dropped my crew off</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1330
00:42:12.864 --> 00:42:14.657  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>at a Maquis base.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1331
00:42:14.657 --> 00:42:18.244  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:46.19%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I</c.mono_sans></c.white><i><c.white><c.mono_sans> had</c.mono_sans></c.white></i><c.white><c.mono_sans> to come back,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1332
00:42:14.657 --> 00:42:18.244  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:61.43%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>but I didn't see any reason</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1333
00:42:18.244 --> 00:42:20.997  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to drag them here</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1334
00:42:18.244 --> 00:42:20.997  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:69.05%  line:84.62% 
