1335
00:42:20.997 --> 00:42:23.500  position:34.76%,start  align:start size:38.57%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You didn't have</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1336
00:42:20.997 --> 00:42:23.500  position:30.95%,start  align:start size:48.10%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>to come back either.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1337
00:42:23.500 --> 00:42:27.170  position:38.57%,start  align:start size:30.95%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Yes. I did.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1338
00:42:27.170 --> 00:42:29.047  position:27.14%,start  align:start size:55.71%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>And I think we both know</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1339
00:42:29.047 --> 00:42:31.966  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:51.90%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>that's why you left us</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1340
00:42:29.047 --> 00:42:31.966  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:42.38%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>alone out there--</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1341
00:42:31.966 --> 00:42:34.719  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:44.29%  line:84.62% 
