1342
00:42:36.513 --> 00:42:40.558  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:61.43%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I'm not going to stand here</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1343
00:42:36.513 --> 00:42:40.558  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:65.24%  line:84.62% 
