1344
00:42:40.558 --> 00:42:43.144  position:32.86%,start  align:start size:44.29%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>You had your duty.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1345
00:42:43.144 --> 00:42:45.230  position:38.57%,start  align:start size:30.95%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I had mine.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1346
00:42:46.564 --> 00:42:48.941  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:50.00%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I still have my duty.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1347
00:42:50.193 --> 00:42:52.487  position:42.38%,start  align:start size:23.33%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I know.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1348
00:42:52.487 --> 00:42:55.865  position:40.48%,start  align:start size:29.05%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>And I know</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1349
00:42:52.487 --> 00:42:55.865  position:23.33%,start  align:start size:61.43%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I'll probably go to prison.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1350
00:42:58.117 --> 00:43:02.038  position:21.43%,start  align:start size:67.14%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>But I came back because of us.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1351
00:43:02.038 --> 00:43:05.208  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:38.57%  line:79.29% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Because despite</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1352
00:43:02.038 --> 00:43:05.208  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:48.10%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>all that's happened,</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1353
00:43:05.208 --> 00:43:07.960  position:29.05%,start  align:start size:51.90%  line:84.62% 
