1354
00:43:10.629 --> 00:43:12.549  position:19.52%,start  align:start size:70.95%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>I don't want to throw that away.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1355
00:43:14.175 --> 00:43:15.468  position:42.38%,start  align:start size:23.33%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>Do you?</c.mono_sans></c.white>

1356
00:43:18.221 --> 00:43:19.764  position:46.19%,start  align:start size:15.71%  line:84.62% 
<c.white><c.mono_sans>No.</c.mono_sans></c.white>

